O-O 12. a4 b4 13. Nd5 Bxd5 14. exd5) (10... O-O 11. a4 Rc8 12. a5 {stopping
Nb6-Nc4}) 11. a4 (11. Qd2 O-O {important move as we can play Nb6 on the next
