-128,-165,-135,-158,-184,-177,-163,-171,-188,-197,-171,-205,-156,-175,-179,
-218,-221] In this game we will explore, White's common mistake 9.f4? and how
to punish it!} 1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 a6 6. h3 (6.
Be3 e5 7. Nb3 Be6 8. h3 Nbd7 {This is our move order!}) (6. a4 e5 7. Nb3 Be7) (
