3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 a6 6. f3 e5 7. Nb3 Be6 8. Be3 h5 9. Nd5 Bxd5 10.
exd5 Nbd7 11. Be2 g6 12. Qd2 $1 (12. O-O {allows} Bh6 13. Bf2) 12... b6 $6 {
a big mistake as now White can castle long!} (12... Bg7) 13. O-O $6 (13. O-O-O
$1 $14 {We can conclude that b6 was a waste of time.}) 13... Bg7 14. a4 O-O 15.
a5 $6 b5 $15 16. c4 bxc4 17. Bxc4 Qc7 $3 {Black knew the plan.} 18. Rfc1 (18.
