Black will push e4.}) 18... Qb7 $3 19. Ra4 Rfc8 $4 {Its a blitz game, mistakes
are common.} (19... Rab8 $1 $17 20. Qe2 Nxd5 $19 (20... e4 $19)) 20. Rb4 Qc7 {
FlorianHandke won by resignation} 1-0

